      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need help writing a rejection email for a candidate. they made it to the final round for a senior dev role here in austin but we decided to go with someone else. they were actually really strong in system design and had great culture fit, so it was a tough call. i want the email to be professional and kind but firm so they dont think there is still a chance. can you draft something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
